Generate a team matching dictionary

Source: R/cbd_match_teams.R
cbd_match_teams.Rd

A utility function that returns a named vector to be used as a matching dictionary.

Usage

cbd_match_teams()

Examples

try(cbd_match_teams()['Duke Blue Devils'])
